  <brief_title>Application of Neurally Adjusted Ventilatory Assist to Children After Congenital Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Application of Neurally Adjusted Ventilatory Assist to Children After Congenital Cardiac Surgery: the Effect of Patient-ventilator Interaction, Gas Exchange and Hemodynamics</official_title>
  <sponsors>
